  "detailed_description": "In Boxing Champion, you can get a magical piece of equipment that you can box, so you can fly out and hit boxing gloves! In order to maximize the space for boxing equipment, we have designed a bottom-up pyramid structure in the scene map, with a total of 7 floors, each of which can make you sweat like a fitness. After the 7th floor, there's the boss encounter, and if you can see it, you'll ask if it's the naughty guy from the 4th series! Haha, no spoilers, come and have a crazy boxing game.",
  "about_the_game": "In Boxing Champion, you can get a magical piece of equipment that you can box, so you can fly out and hit boxing gloves! In order to maximize the space for boxing equipment, we have designed a bottom-up pyramid structure in the scene map, with a total of 7 floors, each of which can make you sweat like a fitness. After the 7th floor, there's the boss encounter, and if you can see it, you'll ask if it's the naughty guy from the 4th series! Haha, no spoilers, come and have a crazy boxing game.",
